Cell["\<\
\[CapitalSigma] (\[Xi], \[ScriptCapitalA]) denotes the tensile stress \
distribution ahead of the fracture obtained from the boundary integral \
equation derived in the paper, whereas \[CapitalSigma]ref (\[Xi], \
\[ScriptCapitalA]) denotes the analytical reference solution derived by \
Atkinson-Craster.\
\>", "Text",
